{"body": "> Removing the code that precompiles the assets without digests, as suggested, is not a possible solution. We need such for emails and similar.\r\n\r\nTo be clear, I wasn't suggesting that the code for creating assets without digests be removed. However if `application.css` and `application-MD5.css` both refer to `image-MD5.png` (and `image.png` is compiled also), then shouldn't that achieve the desired goals?\r\n\r\nI'd prefer to be able to enhance the rake task, so that the same code can work on both 3.1.0 and 3.1.1.", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/comments/2267996", "created_at": "2011-10-03T01:07:35Z", "html_url": "https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/3189#issuecomment-2267996", "updated_at": "2011-10-03T01:07:35Z", "repo": "rails", "issue_id": 3189, "user": {"following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/spohlenz/following{/other_user}", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/spohlenz/events{/privacy}", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/spohlenz/orgs", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/spohlenz", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/spohlenz/gists{/gist_id}", "html_url": "https://github.com/spohlenz", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/spohlenz/subscriptions", "avatar_url": "https://2.gravatar.com/avatar/43da0307752bf635c44c33dcdd962a2e?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2Fd397c2b2be2178fe6247bd50fc97cff2.png", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/spohlenz/repos", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/spohlenz/received_events", "gravatar_id": "43da0307752bf635c44c33dcdd962a2e", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/spohlenz/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "login": "spohlenz", "type": "User", "id": 7600, "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/spohlenz/followers"}, "owner": "rails", "_id": {"$oid": "523839a8bd3543c1510100fd"}, "id": 2267996, "issue_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/3189"}
